<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Instead of:</p>

<p>[foo]
prop1 = 'some value'</p>

<p>[bar]
extends = foo
prop2 = 'some value'</p>

<p>it is proposed that section extension take place in the following way:</p>

<p>[foo]
prop1 = 'some value'</p>

<p>[bar : foo]
prop2 = 'some value'</p>

    </div>
